Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... if you're looking for that mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just keep going up this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Roses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This almost seems like Sleeping Beauty's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Anna... Anna Liebert.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck, Mr. Detective.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If something were to happen to you....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I think of that...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel the same way your mother did, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,An inspector from the German BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,BKA?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to arrest you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty nice hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The old Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I traced all the hospitals they were connected to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you're receiving such treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from the old Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about Inspector Zeman's connection\Nto the secret police and his brutal death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Prague's police chief and two officers\Nwere poisoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The two agents who were sent to tail you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,were found shot to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the chief suspect in all the\Nincidents that have taken place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering all the evidence stacked against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could it be Grimmer, the tall, thin man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who was talking with Inspector Zeman\Nthe day before he was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Mr. Grimmer, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, who is the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who the killer is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew, I wouldn't be in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceived by so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,set up to take the fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,even being on the run from the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be betrayed anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a detective, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have to calmly dissect the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you must calmly uncover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be betrayed anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then start doubting the person\Nyou want to doubt the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see your boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him I want to speak with him about the Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll want to meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.89,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Rose Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge from the German BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm familiar with your background and personal history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also heard rumors about you since the old regime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're practically the head of\Nthe old Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it must be quite difficult to control such\Na large organization these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm envious that you're able to take\Nsuch an extended vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years ago, the secretary for Senator Borzmann,\Nthe German Democratic Party candidate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,committed suicide due to your thorough investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be a little smarter in what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the fool here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you seemed legitimate on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have secretly run this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and acted as the president from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, the frightened citizens see you as you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a smart one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does a smart man like you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as you know, I'm not simply on\Nthis extended vacation for leisure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for the existence of true terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that the illusion you created...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,may have given birth to the devil itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is about the Red Rose Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to investigate quite a bit\Nbefore I found the mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because the author has so many pen names.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Monster Without a Name."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By Emil Scherbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Address, an office in an old building in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, another company is leasing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Klaus Poppe's address was listed as\Nan old farmhouse outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was demolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jakov Vyrobek's was just a rented office, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Every search I run on him comes up with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he must be under your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,An old Czechoslovakian secret police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been consciously trying to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that the mansion ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I never did anything about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's still there, untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,all the political prisoners and researchers\Nheld there vanished one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that wall for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was inside the mansion a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no sign that anyone else\Nhad recently been in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was completely abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the north wall on the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was built rather hastily, as if to hide something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,May I break down that wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you afraid of, Colonel Ranke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we come any closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we may come face to face with true terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nostalgic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You want cream and sugar in your coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, black is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just surprising to have a fan of\NFranz Bonaparta come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your address from Moravia Publishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sovak, you were Bonaparta's editor\Nwhen he was still writing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was only his editor when he was\Ngoing by the pen name Klaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind telling me what he was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to have his work-related\Nmeetings here in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he used to sit in that chair, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He would often play with my daughter in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, my daughter said something rather strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"That man is scary."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter was still little at the time, so she\Nprobably doesn't remember anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he working with the government back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I associated with him assuming that he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his mannerisms, his way of speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the clothes he wore, were all unlike other\Ngovernment VIPs under the old regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he had a gentleness and elegance about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonaparta had a master's in psychology\Nand was a practicing psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also a medical doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,His specialty was brain surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I saw him was... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was the summer of '81 or '82.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he just suddenly showed up at my house one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with a new story...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked somewhat refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A new story...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of story was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A story about a monster falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was like a combination of "Beauty\Nand the Beast" and "Sleeping Beauty."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I rejected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in the doorway just before he left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he turned around and said, "How about this one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Door That Must Never Be Opened."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I asked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"So, on the other side of the door do you find paradise..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"or a monster biding its time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Since the door must never be opened, there's no story..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed, and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you learn anything about Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking what a fine day it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is this the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sovak, I live on Svejk Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy that just visited me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's wanted for a series of murders in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's Japanese... a brain surgeon named Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethanol...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This room reeks of antiseptics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people died here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman from the sketchbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the mother of the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, the older kids will take the soccer field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Milos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal is wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No... he's gonna score!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Milos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Milos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice defense, Milos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved a goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,From the way he's laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he should be all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you going to see Milos and the other boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now why I'm bad at soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to Detective Jan Suk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the prime suspect in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing as being socially blacklisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he turns himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,how can we prove his innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we show that the blonde\Ngirl left the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk must be in the same predicament you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there's only one person who knows all the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hand this over to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Details that only the killer would know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,would make a convincing confession, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you send this to the police, you'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Grimmer returned to Germany before you even knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the police will try to catch him, Grimmer\Nis capable of staying out of their reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he used to be an elite spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll be a suspect for the rest of your\Nlife, and will always be on the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the man named Grimmer\Nnever existed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone gave him that name out of convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Grimmer is a suspect for the rest of his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, what do you think of the decision I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're heading to the Rose Mansion now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You may finally be getting close to your goal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I tell you not to be reckless,\Nit won't change anything, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The promise we made when we\Ncrossed the Czech border...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That if we met again, we'd have another picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishing for rainbow trout, surrounded\Nby beautiful scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,having good wine with good cheese...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be living in fear of that sound from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put some antiseptic on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a boy, bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo Tenma, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like you to come with us...
